\[\frac{d\bm{z}^{m+1}}{d\xi_{i}} =(\bm{W}\frac{d\bm{z}^{m}}{d\xi_{i}}+\eta\bm{\delta}_{i})\circ \sigma_{s_{m}}^{{}^{\prime}}\] (14) \[=\mathrm{diag}(\sigma_{s_{m}}^{{}^{\prime}})(\bm{W}\frac{d\bm{z} ^{m}}{d\xi_{i}}+\eta\bm{\delta}_{i})\] (15)

